<lb n="0158a02"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0158a03"/>
<lb n="0158a04"/><head type="no">No. 1228</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0158a05"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0158001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本，【甲】黃檗版淨嚴等加筆本</note>穢跡金剛說神通大滿陀羅尼法
<lb n="0158a06"/>術靈要門<note n="0158002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">一卷＝經【三】</note><note n="0158002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一卷＝經【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0158002"><lem>一卷</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">經</rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0158a07"/>
<lb n="0158a08"/><byline type="Translator">北天竺國三藏沙門<note n="0158003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔阿質達霰唐言〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0158003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔阿質達霰唐言〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0158003"><lem>阿質
<lb n="0158a09"/>達霰唐言</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>無能勝<note n="0158004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔將〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0158004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔將〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0158004"><lem>將</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>譯</byline>
<lb n="0158a10"/><p>如是我聞。一時佛在拘尸那國力士生處跋
<lb n="0158a11"/>提河邊娑羅雙樹間。爾時如來臨入涅槃。<note n="0158005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔是〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0158005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔是〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0158005"><lem>是</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0158a12"/>時有無量百千萬眾天龍八部人非人等。啼
<lb n="0158a13"/>泣向佛四面哽咽悲惱而住。爾時復有諸天
<lb n="0158a14"/>大眾釋提桓因等。皆來供養。唯有&CB00657;髻梵王。
<lb n="0158a15"/>將諸天女。依於四面圍繞而坐。前後天女<note n="0158006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（百）&M062403;＋千【甲】</note><app n="0158006"><lem>千</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">百千</rdg></app>
<lb n="0158a16"/>萬<note n="0158007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔億〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0158007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔億〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0158007"><lem>億</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>眾。共相娛樂。聞如來<note n="0158008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔入〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0158008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔入〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0158008"><lem>入</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>般涅槃而不
<lb n="0158a17"/>來覲省。時諸大眾為言。今日如來臨般涅槃。
<lb n="0158a18"/>是彼梵王何不來耶。其王必有我慢之心。而
<lb n="0158a19"/>不來至此。我等徒眾驅使小&CB00057;仙。往彼令取。
<lb n="0158a20"/>作是語已策百千眾&CB00057;仙。到於彼處。乃見種
<lb n="0158a21"/>種不淨而為城塹。其仙見已。各犯&CB00057;而死。時
<lb n="0158a22"/>諸大眾怪未曾有。復策無量金剛。亦<note n="0158009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔令〕－【三】</note><note n="0158009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔令〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0158009"><lem>令</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>持
<lb n="0158a23"/>&CB00057;而去。乃至七日無人取得。大眾見是<note n="0158010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">事＋（已）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0158010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">事＋（已）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0158010"><lem>事</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">事已</rdg></app>
<lb n="0158a24"/>倍復悲哀。爾時大眾同聲而說偈言</p>
<lb n="0158a25"/><lg><l>苦哉大聖尊</l><l><note n="0158011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">入真何太＝涅槃一何&M062485;【甲】</note><sic n="0158011" corr="涅槃一何" resp="【甲】">入真何太</sic>速</l>
<lb n="0158a26"/><l>諸天猶決定</l><l><note n="0158012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">天＝無【甲】</note><app n="0158012"><lem>天</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">無</rdg></app>人追喚得</l>
<lb n="0158a27"/><l>痛哉天中天</l><l><note n="0158013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">入真＝涅槃&M062403;【甲】</note><app n="0158013"><lem>入真</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">涅槃</rdg></app>如火滅</l></lg>
<lb n="0158a28"/><p>時諸大眾說此偈已。倍復哽咽悲啼&CB00046;哭。是
<lb n="0158a29"/>時如來愍諸大眾。即以大遍知神力。隨<note n="0158014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">左＋（手）【甲】</note><app n="0158014"><lem>左</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">左手</rdg></app>心
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1228.0158b" n="0158b"/>
<lb n="0158b01"/>化出不壞金剛。即於眾中從座而起。白大眾
<lb n="0158b02"/>言。我有大神&CB00057;能取<note n="0158015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔彼〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0158015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔彼〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0158015"><lem>彼</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>梵王。作是語已即
<lb n="0158b03"/>於大眾<note n="0158016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔之〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0158016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔之〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0158016"><lem>之</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>中顯大神通。變此三千大千世界
<lb n="0158b04"/>六<note n="0158017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">返＝反【三】，變【甲】</note><note n="0158017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">返＝反【宋】【元】【明】，＝變【甲】</note><app n="0158017"><lem>返</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">反</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">變</rdg></app>震動。天宮龍宮諸鬼<note n="0158018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔神〕－【三】</note><note n="0158018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔神〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0158018"><lem>神</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>宮皆悉<note n="0158019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">崩摧＝摧崩【三】【甲】</note><note n="0158019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">崩摧＝摧崩【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0158019"><lem>崩摧</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">摧崩</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0158b05"/>即自騰身至梵王所。以指指之。其彼<note n="0158020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">醜＝種種【三】【甲】</note><note n="0158020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">醜＝種種【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0158020"><lem>醜</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">種種</rdg></app>穢物
<lb n="0158b06"/>變為大<note n="0158021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">地＝池【甲】</note><app n="0158021"><lem>地</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">池</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0158b07"/><p>爾時金剛至彼報言。汝大愚癡我如來欲入
<lb n="0158b08"/>涅槃。汝何不去。<note n="0158022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">即＝耶【三】</note><note n="0158022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">即＝耶【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0158022"><lem>即</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">耶</rdg></app>以金剛不壞之力。微以
<lb n="0158b09"/>指之。梵王發心至如來所</p>
<lb n="0158b10"/><p>爾時大眾讚言。大力士汝能有是神力。取彼
<lb n="0158b11"/>梵王來至於此。時金剛即報言。若有世間眾
<lb n="0158b12"/>生。被諸天惡魔一切外道所惱亂者但誦我&CB00057;
<lb n="0158b13"/>十萬遍。我自現身令一切有情隨意滿足。永
<lb n="0158b14"/>離貧窮常令安樂。其&CB00057;如是。先發此大願。南
<lb n="0158b15"/>無我本師釋迦牟尼佛。於如來滅後受持此
<lb n="0158b16"/>&CB00057;。誓度群生。令佛法不滅久住於世。說是願
<lb n="0158b17"/>已。即說大圓滿陀羅尼神&CB00057;穢跡真言<note n="0158023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔曰〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0158023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔曰〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0158023"><lem>曰</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0158b18"/><p type="dharani"><note n="0158024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（唵&CB03117;…訶））四十二字＝（（唵伐折囉俱嚕陀一麼訶麼羅二訶那娜訶三麼他四微枳羅五尾陀防六沙咩社置羅七藍謨馱羅八烏樞沙麼俱嚕&CB00499;九吽泮吒二合娑婆訶十））&M062403;五十七字【甲】</note><note n="0158024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（（唵&CB03117;…訶））四十<app><lem resp="CBETA.say">三</lem><rdg wit="【大】">二</rdg></app>字＝（（唵伐折囉俱嚕陀一麼訶麼羅二訶那娜訶三麼他四微枳羅五尾陀防六沙咩社置羅七藍謨馱羅八烏樞沙麼俱嚕&CB00499;九吽泮吒二合娑婆訶十））&M062403;五十七字【甲】</note><app n="0158024" word-count="43"><lem>唵&CB03117;咶啒&CB03116;摩訶&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0158025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB03764;＝恨【三】【甲】</note><note n="0158025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB03764;＝恨【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0158025"><lem>&CB03764;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">恨</rdg></app>那&CB04237;<note n="0158026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔三音〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0158026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔三音〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0158026"><lem><note place="inline">三音</note></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>吻
<lb n="0158b19"/><note n="0158027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">汁＝什【三】【甲】</note><note n="0158027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">汁＝什【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0158027"><lem>汁</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">什</rdg></app>吻<note n="0158028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔四音〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0158028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔四音〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0158028"><lem><note place="inline">四音</note></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>微咭微摩那栖<note n="0158029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔六音〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0158029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔六音〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0158029"><lem><note place="inline">六音</note></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>嗚深<note n="0158030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">慕＝暮【三】【甲】</note><note n="0158030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">慕＝暮【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0158030"><lem>慕</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">暮</rdg></app><note n="0158031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔七音〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0158031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔七音〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0158031"><lem><note place="inline">七音</note></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0158b20"/>啒&CB03116;&CB00292;&CB00292;泮泮泮娑訶</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">唵伐折囉俱嚕陀一麼訶麼羅二訶那娜訶三麼他四微枳羅五尾陀防六沙咩社置羅七藍謨馱羅八烏樞沙麼俱嚕&CB00499;九吽泮吒二合娑婆訶十</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0158b21"/><p>時彼金剛說此&CB00057;已。復作是言。我於如來滅
<lb n="0158b22"/>後常誦此&CB00057;。若有眾生<note n="0158032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">請＝情【三】【甲】</note><note n="0158032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">請＝情【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0158032"><lem>請</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">情</rdg></app>願受持此&CB00057;者。我
<lb n="0158b23"/>常為給使者令所求如願。我今於如來前說
<lb n="0158b24"/>此神&CB00057;。<note n="0158033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唯＝惟【三】【甲】</note><note n="0158033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唯＝惟【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0158033"><lem>唯</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">惟</rdg></app>願如來於<note n="0158034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">真＋（際）【三】【甲】，真＝涅槃&M062403;【甲】</note><note n="0158034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">真＋（際）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】，真＝涅槃&M062403;【甲】</note><app n="0158034"><lem>真</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">真際</rdg><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">涅槃</rdg></app>中照知我等。世尊
<lb n="0158b25"/>若有眾生。多被諸惡鬼神之所惱亂。<note n="0158035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（誦）＋此【三】【甲】</note><note n="0158035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（誦）＋此【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0158035"><lem>此</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">誦此</rdg></app>&CB00057;者
<lb n="0158b26"/>皆不能為害。永離苦難。世尊若有善男子善
<lb n="0158b27"/>女人。欲救療萬病者。<note n="0158036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">誦上＝先持此神【三】</note><note n="0158036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">誦上＝先持此神【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0158036"><lem>誦上</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">先持此神</rdg></app>&CB00057;四十萬遍。見
<lb n="0158b28"/>有病者治之有驗。無問淨與不淨隨意驅使。
<lb n="0158b29"/>我當隨從滿一切願。若欲令枯樹生枝葉者。
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1228.0158c" n="0158c"/>
<lb n="0158c01"/>取白膠香一大兩。塗樹心。楊枝&CB00057;樹一百遍。
<lb n="0158c02"/>日三時至滿三日即生華果。若欲令枯泉出
<lb n="0158c03"/>水者。淨灰圍之。<note n="0158037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">即＝取【三】【甲】</note><note n="0158037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">即＝取【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0158037"><lem>即</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">取</rdg></app>井華水三<note n="0158038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">斗＝升【三】【甲】下同</note><note n="0158038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">斗＝升【宋】【元】【明】【甲】下同</note><app n="0158038"><lem>斗</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">升</rdg></app>置泉<note n="0158039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔水〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0158039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔水〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0158039"><lem>水</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0158c04"/>中。於寅時&CB00057;一百八遍。水如車輪涌出。若欲
<lb n="0158c05"/>令枯山生草木。取<note n="0158040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鑌＝賓【三】【甲】</note><note n="0158040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鑌＝賓【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0158040"><lem>鑌</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">賓</rdg></app>鐵刀一口。於四方圍
<lb n="0158c06"/>山。&CB00057;三千遍七日滿<note n="0158041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">則＝即【三】【甲】</note><note n="0158041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">則＝即【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0158041"><lem>則</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">即</rdg></app>生。若欲令野獸歸伏
<lb n="0158c07"/>者。取安<note n="0158042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">悉＝息【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0158042"><lem>悉</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">息</rdg></app>香燒向有獸住處&CB00057;一千遍。其獸
<lb n="0158c08"/>至夜間。並集持法人門首。歸降如人間六畜
<lb n="0158c09"/>相似。隨意驅使永不相捨。<note n="0158043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">若＋（欲）【三】【甲】＊</note><note n="0158043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">若＋（欲）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0158043"><lem>若</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">若欲</rdg></app>令夜叉自來歸
<lb n="0158c10"/>降者。取<note n="0158044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">桃＋（柳）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0158044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">桃＋（柳）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0158044"><lem>桃</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">桃柳</rdg></app>枝十翦齊截。取水一<note n="0158045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">石＝碩【三】【甲】</note><note n="0158045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">石＝碩【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0158045"><lem>石</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">碩</rdg></app>煎取五
<lb n="0158c11"/>斗。澇桃柳枝出。以丁香三大兩乳頭香三大
<lb n="0158c12"/>兩白膠香三大兩。<note n="0158046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">後＝復【甲】</note><app n="0158046"><lem>後</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">復</rdg></app>和柳水煎取五斗。即置
<lb n="0158c13"/>一破盆中。取一桃枝長三<note n="0158047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">尺＝赤【宋】【元】</note><app n="0158047"><lem>尺</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">赤</rdg></app>。攪水誦&CB00057;一百
<lb n="0158c14"/>遍。一切夜叉羅剎皆來現。共行法人語。請求
<lb n="0158c15"/>與人<note n="0158048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">先＝充【三】【甲】</note><note n="0158048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">先＝充【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0158048"><lem>先</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">充</rdg></app>為侍者。若令諸惡鬼神毒蛇蝎猛獸
<lb n="0158c16"/>等毒<note n="0158049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以＝心【甲】</note><app n="0158049"><lem>以</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">心</rdg></app>滅者。取淨灰圍所居穴孔。<note n="0158050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">並＝普【元】【明】</note><app n="0158050"><lem>並</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">普</rdg></app>自出
<lb n="0158c17"/>來。當微出聲&CB00057;之一百遍。其蛇等一切<note n="0158051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蠱＝蟲【三】【甲】</note><note n="0158051" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蠱＝蟲【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0158051"><lem>蠱</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">蟲</rdg></app>
<lb n="0158c18"/>獸。各滅毒心不敢傷人。速得解脫。若令惡
<lb n="0158c19"/><note n="0158052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">狗＝鬼【三】</note><note n="0158052" resp="CBETA" type="mod">狗＝鬼【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0158052"><lem>狗</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">鬼</rdg></app>不傷人者。取食一搏&CB00057;七遍與食。永不傷
<lb n="0158c20"/>人復不出<note n="0158053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">聲＋（又法若令惡鬼自歸降人者取水三斗盛於銅器中取淨灰俵之默誦此&CB00057;一百八遍其鬼自來歸於人也）&M062403;【甲】</note><app n="0158053"><lem>聲</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">聲又法若令惡鬼自歸降人者取水三斗盛於銅器中取淨灰俵之默誦此&CB00057;一百八遍其鬼自來歸於人也</rdg></app>。<app type="＊" source="0158043"><lem>若</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">若欲</rdg></app>令惡人來降伏者。書前人
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1228.0159a" n="0159a"/>
<lb n="0159a01"/>姓名置&CB00057;人&CB00560;下。&CB00057;之百遍。心念彼人其人
<lb n="0159a02"/>立至。降伏捨怨憎之<note n="0159001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">心＋（又法若令前人不信者誦&CB00057;一百八遍其人即生怨恨若令如故者依前法）&M062403;【甲】</note><app n="0159001"><lem>心</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">心又法若令前人不信者誦&CB00057;一百八遍其人即生怨恨若令如故者依前法</rdg></app>。若<note n="0159002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">欲＋（令）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0159002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">欲＋（令）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159002"><lem>欲</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">欲令</rdg></app>人相憎者。書
<lb n="0159a03"/>彼二人名號。於自足下&CB00057;二百一十<note n="0159003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">八＝六&M062485;【甲】</note><sic n="0159003" corr="六" resp="【甲】">八</sic>遍。其
<lb n="0159a04"/>人等便相離背不相愛敬。若有相憎人令相
<lb n="0159a05"/>愛敬者。即書取彼名姓。於自足下&CB00057;一百八
<lb n="0159a06"/>遍。其人便相愛重永不相捨。若有未安樂之
<lb n="0159a07"/>人令安樂者。取前人名字書足下。&CB00057;三百遍。
<lb n="0159a08"/>當為彼人發大誓願。我於彼時即自<note n="0159004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">送＋（無量珍寶施與彼貧人悉得充足又法若持&CB00057;人求種種智求種種慧者但誦&CB00057;十萬遍自得種種大智慧種種為善）&M062403;【甲】</note><app n="0159004"><lem>送</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">送無量珍寶施與彼貧人悉得充足又法若持&CB00057;人求種種智求種種慧者但誦&CB00057;十萬遍自得種種大智慧種種為善</rdg></app>。辯才
<lb n="0159a09"/>無滯隨行者意。所須之者並悉施與。若持&CB00057;
<lb n="0159a10"/>人求種種珍寶摩尼如意珠等者。但至心誦
<lb n="0159a11"/>&CB00057;自限多少。我即自送滿其所願。若欲治人
<lb n="0159a12"/>病者。作頓病印。先以左手頭指中指。<note n="0159005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">押索＝屈押房素&M062403;【甲】</note><app n="0159005"><lem>押索</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">屈押房素</rdg></app>
<lb n="0159a13"/>文。<note n="0159006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">印＝即【三】【甲】</note><note n="0159006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">印＝即【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159006"><lem>印</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">即</rdg></app>&CB00057;之一百遍以印頓病人七下立差。若
<lb n="0159a14"/>病人臨欲死者。先<note n="0159007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">於＝作【甲】</note><app n="0159007"><lem>於</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">作</rdg></app>禁五路印然後治之。即
<lb n="0159a15"/>不死印<note n="0159008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">目＝自【元】【明】【甲】，日&M062403;【甲】</note><note n="0159008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">目＝自【元】【明】【甲】，＝日&M062403;【甲】</note><app n="0159008"><lem>目</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">自</rdg><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">日</rdg></app>。如是先<note n="0159009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（以）＋准【三】【甲】</note><note n="0159009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（以）＋准【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159009"><lem>准</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">以准</rdg></app><note n="0159010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">印＝前&M062403;【甲】</note><app n="0159010"><lem>印</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">前</rdg></app>以無名指屈向掌
<lb n="0159a16"/>中。&CB00594;小指&CB00057;之<note n="0159011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">百＋（八）&M062403;【甲】</note><app n="0159011"><lem>百</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">百八</rdg></app>遍其患速除</p>
<lb n="0159a17"/><p>若治邪病者。但於病患人頭邊。燒安<app type="＊" source="0158042"><lem>悉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">息</rdg></app>香誦
<lb n="0159a18"/>之。&CB00057;立除之。若<note n="0159012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蟲＝治蠱【三】【甲】</note><note n="0159012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蟲＝治蠱【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159012"><lem>蟲</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">治蠱</rdg></app>毒病<note n="0159013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔者〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0159013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔者〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159013"><lem>者</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。書患人名字紙
<lb n="0159a19"/>上&CB00057;之即差。<note n="0159014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（若）＋治【三】【甲】</note><note n="0159014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（若）＋治【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159014"><lem>治</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">若治</rdg></app>精魅病者亦<note n="0159015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">如＋（上）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0159015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">如＋（上）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159015"><lem>如</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">如上</rdg></app>法。若治伏
<lb n="0159a20"/>連病者。書患人姓名及作病鬼姓名。埋患人
<lb n="0159a21"/>床下&CB00057;之。其鬼<note n="0159016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">遠＝速【三】【甲】</note><note n="0159016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">遠＝速【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159016"><lem>遠</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">速</rdg></app>奉名字自出現身。便令彼
<lb n="0159a22"/>鬼看三世之事。一一具說向人其病速差。若
<lb n="0159a23"/>有<note n="0159017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（人）＋患【三】【甲】</note><note n="0159017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（人）＋患【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159017"><lem>患</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">人患</rdg></app>時氣病者。&CB00057;師見之即差。若欲令行病
<lb n="0159a24"/>鬼王不入界者。於十齋日誦我此&CB00057;一千八
<lb n="0159a25"/>遍。能除<note n="0159018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">萬里＝百萬&M062403;【甲】</note><app n="0159018"><lem>萬里</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">百萬</rdg></app><note n="0159019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">病＝衰【三】【甲】</note><note n="0159019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">病＝衰【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159019"><lem>病</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">衰</rdg></app>患</p>
<lb n="0159a26"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead>穢跡金剛說神通大滿陀羅尼法術靈要門
